As I suspected, the problem was in `timestamp` which Hibernate / JDBC was not able to convert to Instant. I&#39;ve solved it by converting timestamp to varchar in SQL and change the type in Java interface to String.
```Java
@Query(value = &quot;select ti.id, convert(varchar, ti.timestamp, 120) as timestamp, ti.fuel_station_id, ti.cash_register_id, sum(cast(dsc.discount as numeric(12,2))) as saving
from transaction_info as ti
